game.rock_paper_scissors.details:
f%最经典的石头剪刀布游戏，家喻户晓。

{tc:yellow}克制关系：{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}剪刀{tc:clear} > {tc:gray}布{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}布{tc:clear} > {tc:gray}石头{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}石头{tc:clear} > {tc:gray}剪刀{tc:clear}

{tc:yellow}操作提示：{tc:clear}
{tc:light_cyan}[1]{tc:clear} 出剪刀
{tc:light_cyan}[2]{tc:clear} 出石头
{tc:light_cyan}[3]{tc:clear} 出布
{tc:light_cyan}[R]{tc:clear} 重新开始
{tc:light_cyan}[Q]/[ESC]{tc:clear} 退出
